==English==

==Noun==

==Meaning==

#''Phonetics.'' A type of consonantal sound that is produced by vibrations of the tongue against the place of articulation, for example, Spanish ''rr''.
#''Music.'' A rapid alternation between an indicated note and the one above it, usually indicated with the letters ''tr'' written above the staff.

